data.description: If are you looking for space..well you found it. This home features 4 Bedrooms 2.5 Baths. A large bonus room that could be the man cave or a kids playroom. The chefs kitchen is a dream with an island and a wine bar that also has a desk. Walk in pantry as well. Kitchen also features granite counter tops and backsplash.The large island is perfect for entertaining while you cook. You will find a large living room with a stack stone fireplace. The formal dining can host all those family dinners, features a coffered ceiling. An additional space downstairs could be used for an office offers privacy with its French Doors. The primary bedroom has a double trey ceiling, walk in closet. A primary bath that is large enough for all your needs. Primary Bath features   double vanity, tile shower and separate tub. The covered deck looks out over this spacious lot with a fully fenced yard. Currently NO HOA.
